{"segment_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-001", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan", "source_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 甘誓 [1]", "text_original": "啟與有扈戰于甘之野，作《甘誓》。", "text_normalized": "啟與有扈戰于甘之野，作《甘誓》。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-002", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan", "source_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 甘誓 [2]", "text_original": "大戰于甘，乃召六卿。", "text_normalized": "大戰于甘，乃召六卿。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-003", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan", "source_id": "shangshu-009-xia-shu-speech-at-gan__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 甘誓 [3]", "text_original": "王曰：「嗟！六事之人，予誓告汝：有扈氏威侮五行，怠棄三正，天用勦絕其命。今予惟恭行天之罰。左不攻于左，汝不恭命；右不攻于右，汝不恭命；御非其馬之正，汝不恭命。用命，賞于祖；弗用命，戮于社。予則孥戮汝。」", "text_normalized": "王曰：「嗟！六事之人，予誓告汝：有扈氏威侮五行，怠棄三正，天用勦絕其命。今予惟恭行天之罰。左不攻于左，汝不恭命；右不攻于右，汝不恭命；御非其馬之正，汝不恭命。用命，賞于祖；弗用命，戮于社。予則孥戮汝。」", "notes": ""}
